#

Pumpkin Waffles

25 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianhigh fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

breakfastbruncheasyfall flavors

Description

Deliciously fluffy pumpkin waffles, perfect for breakfast or brunch, with a hint of warm spices.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 1/2 cups
  • pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2 large
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • cinnamon: 1 tsp
  • nutmeg: 1/4 tsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • butter (melted): 1/4 cup
